column3: If this is visible in the UI it should be translated and use more descriptive message or a sentence IMHO.\n
Great idea. Any suggestion for a  default?\n
This is a test option, let's not  burden translators with this.\n

I actually think it should _not_ be translated.  Translating it will break software which is attempting to use it. This field is not generally for human reading, but e.g. automatic tests of your alterting infrastructure would happily key on the specific text.\n
